  <str key="2827543010-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="2827543010">A siege unit ruptured by the Elysium Fault, reemerging as 'The Maw of Silence'. She does not advance, she consumes. Her steps fracture fortifications. Her hunger ends engagements.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"Every fortress feeds the fire that will melt it." - Golem Suneater&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color="#dc9c36"&gt;Wearable by Heavy Assault. NSO use only.&lt;/font&gt;</str>
