  <str key="2881028722-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="2881028722">Something lurks below, or above or BEHIND YOU!  Give yourself an ominous presence on the battlefield with this horn.  All factions can use this gear.</str>
  <str key="2920225520-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="2920225520">A remotely controlled unmanned aerial vehicle designed to detect the enemy and provide battlefield overview. The range is limited to 60 meters. The recon drone's battery life is 40 seconds. </str>
