  <str key="2965198848-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="2965198848">An infrastructure specialist reborn in the Elysium Fault as 'The Voice Of Undoing'. Her syllables short circuit systems, her every whisper, sabotage.  When she speaks, machines remember how to die.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"Why fix what should never have been built?" - Breaker Vox&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color="#dc9c36"&gt;Wearable by Engineer. NSO use only.&lt;/font&gt;</str>
  <str key="2969287676-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="2969287676">A machine with the voices of the fallen echoing through her circuits, drowned in memory. Reborn as "The Hymn of Hollowing", her nanites restore the body but erode the soul. The risen may live to fight another day, but never as they were.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"The dead sing louder than the living ever will" - Choral Hollow&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color="#dc9c36"&gt;Wearable by Combat Medic. NSO use only.&lt;/font&gt;</str>
